Recommended the Management to require the Municipal Treasurer to strictly observe the guidelines in the granting, utilization and liquidation of CA as provided under COA Circular No. 97-002, specifically:
     a) Ensure that granting of cash advance to accountable officer is for a specific purpose;
     b) Ensure that the cash advance is used solely for the specific legal purpose for which it was granted;
     c) Discontinue the practice of granting of cash advances to accountable officers with unliquidated balance; and
     d) Forbid the transfer of cash advance from one accountable officer to another.

